<br>
Anyway - I can't find the guide to quadding these bad boys anywhere. Now, I know how to pull em' and I am an expert quadder, but the guide had some info I would seriously like to compare with my own experience. Specifically - how much % regular XP / AA XP should these guys give in 57?<br>
